revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yarbros}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yarbro'' is the 20364<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 1305 individuals. ''Yarbro'' is most common among White (82.38%) and Black/African American (13.41%) individuals.
